    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You may break a weapon when attacking a creature to deal 1d4 points of additional damage on that attack. This damage is multiplied on a critical hit. This additional damage increases by an additional 1d4 for every 4 base attack bonus you possess.</p>\n<p>If you threaten a critical hit while using this talent, you gain a +4 bonus on the roll to confirm the critical hit, and if it is confirmed, the weapon is destroyed. If you apply a second effect that would give your weapon the broken condition, you forgo this additional benefit. <strong>Associated Feat:</strong> Chairbreaker.</p>\n",
